		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Interviewer: "Thank you for sharing that. It’s great to hear that you’re looking for a fulfilling career. We value team members who are committed to their growth and happiness. Before we wrap up, do you have any questions for me about the role or the company?"</turn>
